Package: MAFI
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Signal Aggregate Funnel Index for Publication Bias Detection
Version: 2.2.0
Date: 2025-01-12
Authors@R: c(
    person("MAFI", "Development Team", email = "mafi@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A publication bias detection tool that clusters correlated statistical
    signals into a calibrated probability score (0-100). Version 2.2.0 addresses
    methodological concerns: (1) signals grouped into clusters (asymmetry, selection,
    excess significance, trim-fill) to avoid double-counting correlated measures,
    (2) high heterogeneity (I-squared) now INCREASES suspicion (reversed from v2.1),
    (3) small-n reliability handled via CI widening rather than point estimate penalty,
    (4) validation includes null effect (theta=0) simulations for specificity testing,
    (5) calibration slope metric added. The package provides bootstrap confidence
    intervals, Bonferroni-adjusted selection model tests, and ensemble-corrected
    effect estimates. Use validate_mafi() to assess performance.
